title: Bart Whitaker // 33
description:
When a desperate neighbor calls 911 in hopes of saving the beloved family next door from a shooting, only 2 out of 4 survive. But after the eldest son is questioned in the hospital, police become incredibly suspicious. Then, an important tip comes into the station that turns this case upside down and solidifies the detective's inkling. This is the case of Bart Whitaker.
